item.title: One Plus 5 Smart Review
item.description: OnePlus 5, reviewing this phone gives me lot of satisfaction as i am a big fan of OnePlus phones whether its any variant of One Plus. I must tell you buying this phone is worth for its price and you wont’t regret it. Last year the company had launced OnePlus 3T which made huge profit for the company almost in every country wherever it was launched.
